### 0) Проверка: server reflection (просто чтобы понять, что порт живой)
GRPC localhost:9090/grpc.reflection.v1alpha.ServerReflection/ServerReflectionInfo
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "host": "localhost",
  "list_services": ""
}

###

### CreateNotificationEvent (SCHEDULED) — sendAt строкой
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CreateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-create-002",
  "templateId": "reminder",
  "templateVersion": 2,
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_HIGH",
  "preferredChannel": "CHANNEL_PUSH",
  "strategy": {
    "kind": "STRATEGY_KIND_SCHEDULED",
    "sendAt": "2026-02-25T00:30:00Z"
  },
  "payload": { "title": "Reminder", "body": "Don't forget!" },
  "audience": { "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT", "snapshotOnDispatch": true }
}


### 1) CreateNotificationEvent (IMMEDIATE)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CreateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-create-001",
  "templateId": "welcome-email",
  "templateVersion": 1,
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_NORMAL",
  "preferredChannel": "CHANNEL_EMAIL",
  "strategy": {
    "kind": "STRATEGY_KIND_IMMEDIATE"
  },
  "payload": {
    "firstName": "Armen",
    "promo": "WELCOME10"
  },
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true,
    "recipientId": [
      "user-1001",
      "user-1002"
    ]
  }
}

###

### 2) CreateNotificationEvent (SCHEDULED)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CreateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-create-002",
  "templateId": "reminder",
  "templateVersion": 2,
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_HIGH",
  "preferredChannel": "CHANNEL_PUSH",
  "strategy": {
    "kind": "STRATEGY_KIND_SCHEDULED",
    "sendAt": { "seconds": 1772000000, "nanos": 0 }
  },
  "payload": {
    "title": "Reminder",
    "body": "Don't forget!"
  },
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true
  }
}

###

### 3) GetNotificationEvent (подставь event_id из CreateEventResponse)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/GetNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}"
}

###

### 4) UpdateNotificationEvent (FieldMask: priority + payload)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/UpdateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "updateMask": { "paths": ["priority", "payload"] },
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_LOW",
  "payload": {
    "firstName": "Armen",
    "promo": "WELCOME20"
  }
}

###

### 5) SetAudience (переключить на GROUPS — если реализовано, иначе получишь FAILED_PRECONDITION/UNIMPLEMENTED)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/SetAudience
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_GROUPS",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true,
    "groupId": ["group-vip", "group-new-users"]
  }
}

###

### 6) SetAudience (EXPLICIT пустая, потом добавим через AddRecipients)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/SetAudience
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true
  }
}

###

### 7) AddRecipients (батч)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/AddRecipients
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-addrecipients-001",
  "recipientId": ["user-2001", "user-2002", "user-2003"]
}

###

### 8) GetAudience
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/GetAudience
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}"
}

###

### 9) RemoveRecipients
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/RemoveRecipients
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "recipientId": ["user-2002"]
}

###

### 10) TriggerDispatch (MANUAL / IMMEDIATE event — создаст dispatch)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/TriggerDispatch
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "idem-dispatch-001"
}

###

### 11) GetDispatch (подставь dispatch_id из TriggerDispatchResponse)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/GetDispatch
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "dispatchId": "{{dispatch_id}}"
}

###

### 12) ListDispatches (по event_id)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/ListDispatches
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "page": 0,
  "size": 20
}

###

### 13) ListNotificationEvents (по клиенту из auth)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/ListNotificationEvents
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "page": 0,
  "size": 20,
  "statusFilter": "EVENT_STATUS_UNSPECIFIED"
}

###

### 14) CancelNotificationEvent (event_id)
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CancelNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers
# authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id}}",
  "reason": "test cancel"
}

###
### =========================
### MAIL FLOW: 3 new events -> audience -> dispatch -> Kafka
### Запускать сверху вниз. IntelliJ HTTP Client сохранит `event_id_*` и `dispatch_id_*`.
### =========================

### A1) CreateNotificationEvent
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CreateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-{{$timestamp}}-1",
  "templateId": "welcome-email",
  "templateVersion": 1,
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_NORMAL",
  "preferredChannel": "CHANNEL_EMAIL",
  "strategy": {
    "kind": "STRATEGY_KIND_IMMEDIATE"
  },
  "payload": {
    "campaign": "spring-batch-a1",
    "title": "Welcome A1",
    "body": "First mail event from grpc curl"
  },
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true
  }
}
> {% client.global.set("event_id_1", response.body.eventId); %}

###
### A2) AddRecipients
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/AddRecipients
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id_1}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-add-{{$timestamp}}-1",
  "recipientId": [
    "mail-user-1001",
    "mail-user-1002"
  ]
}

###
### A3) TriggerDispatch -> создаст dispatch и отправит mail_dispatch в Kafka
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/TriggerDispatch
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id_1}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-dispatch-{{$timestamp}}-1"
}
> {% client.global.set("dispatch_id_1", response.body.dispatchId); %}

###
### B1) CreateNotificationEvent
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/CreateNotificationEvent
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-{{$timestamp}}-2",
  "templateId": "promo-email",
  "templateVersion": 1,
  "priority": "DELIVERY_PRIORITY_HIGH",
  "preferredChannel": "CHANNEL_EMAIL",
  "strategy": {
    "kind": "STRATEGY_KIND_IMMEDIATE"
  },
  "payload": {
    "campaign": "spring-batch-b1",
    "title": "Promo B1",
    "body": "Second mail event from grpc curl",
    "promoCode": "WELCOME15"
  },
  "audience": {
    "kind": "AUDIENCE_KIND_EXPLICIT",
    "snapshotOnDispatch": true
  }
}
> {% client.global.set("event_id_2", response.body.eventId); %}

###
### B2) AddRecipients
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/AddRecipients
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id_2}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-add-{{$timestamp}}-2",
  "recipientId": [
    "mail-user-1003",
    "mail-user-1004",
    "mail-user-1005"
  ]
}

###
### B3) TriggerDispatch
GRPC localhost:9090/notification.facade.v1.NotificationFacade/TriggerDispatch
Content-Type: application/grpc
TE: trailers

{
  "eventId": "{{event_id_2}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "mail-batch-dispatch-{{$timestamp}}-2"
}
> {% client.global.set("dispatch_id_2", response.body.dispatchId); %}

###
### C1) CreateNotificationEvent
